{"tid":902224,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"尹恩惠靚樣不復再！","createTime":"2018-11-14T15:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T19:38:04.000Z","uid":160973,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"beb31eab8bde883e319b4dca081fcc843a01a8cb","tid":902224,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"34歲韓國女演員尹恩惠15年在內地出演設計綜藝節目陷入抄襲風波，事隔3年最近復出接拍的小說改編劇集《心動警報》，暌違公仔箱5年可惜依然一片負評，其中被狠批得最厲害的，就是她整形後的一副膠面！<br />\n<br />\n99年以15歲之齡出道的尹恩惠，05年離開女團Baby V.O.X正式開展演戲之路，拍過不少為港人熟悉的劇集，包括10多年前的成名作《宮》和《咖啡王子》，以及之後的《千億寵愛在一身》、《大話男女》、《想念你》、《未來的選擇》等，氣質美女形象深入民心，現在卻因為整形過度完全失去當初清純脫俗的味道，不少看着她成長的劇迷都非常可惜，唯有回顧一下她過往的美貌，懷念一下吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2TdxiML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TdxiML&d=d7VJPFS6CXfBo3B1q4wvF5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a64598df\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2TdxiML</a>"},{"pid":"c9ef8cd0f65752860b30e139752d82f794c76247","tid":902224,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"泡菜都係攞膠造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe67d6a704fc039b168199250ddd8db36bb8c8c","tid":902224,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"5e05e90bf9c4b975aee9a563fd6093cc8226e878","tid":902224,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:27:56.000Z","msg":"以前好中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc089d807cb68153b62482ecd465e8cc30eb669","tid":902224,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T19:38:04.000Z","msg":"邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}